{"type":null,"faqId":11990,"title":"G620-L72  如何节省移动数据流量？","answer":"<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">有</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络时，请优先使用</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络。</span> \n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不使用移动网络的数据业务时，请关闭数据业务。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">打开通知面板，点击<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33392\" /></span></span></span><span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，快速关闭数据业务。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">浏览网页时，若不需要显示网页上的图片，可以选择屏蔽网页图片。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在“浏览器”界面，打开选项菜单，点击“设置</span><span> &gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">带宽管理”，取消勾选“载入图片”复选框。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33393\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">禁止应用程序通过移动网络上网。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">在“设置”界面，点击“联网应用”，选择要限制上网权限的应用程序，点击对应的<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33394\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33395\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">如无必要，请关闭后台数据同步。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 打开通知面板，然后点击<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33396\" /></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33397\" /></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33398\" /></span></span> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2796","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398824449000,"seriesProductName":"G620-L72","visitedTimes":61,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"如何节省移动数据流量","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}